videos.description: Georgia's Yante Maten takes the pass from William Jackson II and spins past Tennessee defenders then sinks the layup while getting fouled.
videos.headline: Georgia's Maten spins past defenders for and-1

videos.description: Tennessee's Jordan Bone takes the ball from beyond half court then speeds past three Georgia defenders for the layup.
videos.headline: Bone breezes past Georgia defenders for 2

videos.description: Tennessee's Admiral Schofield jumps up for a defensive rebound but slams down on the hardwood and is reluctant to get up. Schofield would eventually return to the game.
videos.headline: Schofield goes down hard in a scary moment

videos.description: After a missed 3-pointer by Georgia's William Jackson II, Derek Ogbeide snags the offensive rebound over Tennessee defenders then tosses in the 2-point shot to redeem his teammate.
videos.headline: Georgia's Ogbeide overpowers defenders for putback

videos.description: Georgia's William Jackson II finds a wide-open Derek Ogbeide who throws down the dunk, extending the Bulldogs' lead.
videos.headline: Ogbeide throws it down to extend Georgia's lead

videos.description: Georgia's Yante Maten posts up then moves to the basket while slipping through a slew of Tennessee defenders for a crafty layup.
videos.headline: Georgia's Maten weaves through defenders for fancy layup

videos.description: Georgia's Derek Ogbeide bobbles a pass from Nicolas Claxton, ducks through 2 defenders then completes his and-1 layup by striking a pose.
videos.headline: Georgia's Ogbeide sinks and-1 then strikes a pose

videos.description: With under 2 minutes to go, Tyree Crump drains a deep 3-pointer to extend Georgia's lead and ultimately give them the victory.
videos.headline: Crump's back-breaking three helps seal the win for Georgia

videos.description: Forward Yante Maten leads the Bulldogs' five double-figure scorers with 19 points while Derek Ogbeide secures a double-double in the upset over the Vols.
videos.headline: Maten, UGA step up in 73-62 win vs. No. 18 Tennessee

videos.description: Yante Maten scores a team-high 19 points as the Bulldogs defeat the No. 18 Volunteers 73-62 at home.
videos.headline: Georgia takes down No. 18 Tennessee
